  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00001",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "貂蝉上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00002",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "坐着绣梧桐，芭蕉开玉屏。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00003",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "奴乃貂蝉，王老爷府下为奴。每日吹弹歌舞，也不是俺女流生活。只因圣上相府设筵，庆贺文武百官，可恨董卓父子，在朝专权，害死张老爷，满朝文武，并无一人搭救。奴乃女流之辈，说之无益，不免去到花园，游玩散心。",
      "text_length": 99
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00004",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "心儿灵来性儿巧，丢下琥珀弄玉箫。王老爷看我如珍宝，一班女乐令我教。身穿一件红绫袄，白绫裙儿紧束腰。董卓贼在朝行霸道，何日杀贼把冤消？行一步来才把花园进，来到花园看分晓。耳旁猛听人喝道，想必老爷他来到。将身且躲花荫下，等他来时诉根苗。",
      "text_length": 116
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00005",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王允上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00006",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "汉室江山四百年，出了董卓乱朝班。相府设下百官宴，可怜我张年兄立丧席前。在那里我不敢倾滴泪眼，怕的是奸贼解机关。王允低头进花园，扭回头来把门关。见太湖石前长松柏，又观见那边厢长的穿枝莲。弯弯曲曲过甬道，绕梁燕子闹声喧。行过牡丹亭一座，养鱼池中水绕莲。水流千澜还相见，张年兄一见永不还。回首来观见树上鸟，那鸟儿绕来绕去在枝间。那鸟儿为的是嘴边食，我王允为的是汉室江山。",
      "text_length": 182
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00007",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "貂蝉哭。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00008",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "哭一声屈死的张老爷，恨只恨董卓、吕奉先。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00009",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "耳旁里猛听得人言语，扭回头来见貂蝉。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00010",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "唗！貂蝉，花园乃老爷幽雅所在，岂是你偷情之处？",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00011",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "小丫鬟怎敢偷情？是我心中恨着一人，可惜着一人。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00012",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "你恨着哪个，可惜的是谁？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00013",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "可恨董卓父子，在朝专权，害死张老爷，满朝文武，并无一人搭救。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00014",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "汉室四百年天下，今出在貂蝉口中。貂蝉，你乃女流之辈，能把他怎的？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00015",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "小丫鬟若有进身之路，情愿与张老爷复仇。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00016",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "貂蝉，此处非讲话所在，随爷去到书阁。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00017",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "星月下见貂蝉十分美貌，她好似天仙女降下九霄。汉王允进书阁心生巧计，貂蝉女向前来细听根苗。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00018",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "貂蝉，爷有一言，从不从，莫要介意。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00019",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "老爷有何教谕，但请讲来。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00020",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "我有心将你明许吕布，暗献董卓。或卓或布，杀死一个，老爷好保汉室江山。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00021",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "尽在老爷。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00022",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "既然如此，貂蝉转上，受爷一拜。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00023",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "王司徒提罗衣跪在花园，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00024",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "貂蝉女进前来细听我言：清晨起爷去到相府饮宴，虎牢关来了个温侯奉先。董卓贼一见了怒生满面，可怜你张老爷立丧席前。满朝里随董卓就有大半，惟有你王老爷是个忠官。心儿里要杀贼未得其便，无一个妙人儿保汉江山。",
      "text_length": 99
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00025",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "心里忧来闷悠悠，何日才展放眉头？有美酒来难消受，琴瑟难解君子愁。我与你连环又成就，即要把汉室江山挂心头。怕的是情儿厚薄你把机关漏，你老爷满门难保周。",
      "text_length": 74
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00026",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "貂蝉"
      ],
      "text": "碧玉连环方成就，王老爷且展双眉头。这一人相府遇邂逅，我不杀董卓定杀温侯。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00027",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "貂蝉下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01017012_e00028",
      "play_id": "01017012",
      "scene_id": "01017012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "见貂蝉行走甚风流，司徒王允放心头。连环计儿成就了，要保汉室万千秋。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
